                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17871212-68-off325 t17871212-68-cd326"></join> last, a chesnut gelding, value 13 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17871212-68-victim585" type="victimName">
                     Jonathan 
                     Pegram
